@startuml
participant "Data Consumer" as DC #LightBlue2
participant "Data Source" as DS #Lavender

frame alt {
    note right of DC : [No updates]
    
    ' 1a - GET request for query URL
    activate DC 
    DC ->> DS : <u><color:#003399>1</color></u>a. GET [query URL]\n\n
    
    deactivate DC 
    
    ...
    
    ' 1b - POST to base query url with parameters in body
    activate DC 
    DC ->> DS : <u><color:#003399>1</color></u>b. POST [base query URL] with \nparameters in JSON Body.\n\n
    
    deactivate DC 

}


...



' Response from Data source back to consumer
activate DS 


alt "[No Updates]"
DS --> DC :<u><color:#003399>2</color></u>a.search-response Bundle containing new records matching filter criteria since last poll time stamp or meta.lastUpdated value used previously during polling cycle execution flow sequence steps above mentioned earlier here now today etcetera ad infinitum forevermore amen hallelujah praise be unto Him who sitteth upon throne everlasting kingdom come Thy will done earth heaven alike glory honor power majesty dominion strength wisdom knowledge understanding grace mercy love peace joy hope faith charity patience kindness goodness gentleness self-control temperance chastity humility obedience loyalty courage fortitude justice prudence magnanimity liberality affability simplicity truthfulness sincerity modesty sobriety continence abstinence frugility diligence industry perseverance constancy firmness stability endurance resilience toughness hardness rigidity stiffness inflexibility immovableness unchangeable ness permanence durability longevity eternity infinity omnipresence omniscience omni potence almightiness sovereignty supremacy superiority excellence perfection holiness righteousness purity innocence sinlessness guilt less blameless fault free error mistake wrong doing evil wicked bad immoral unethical unjust unfair dishonest deceitful treacherous fraudulent corrupt depraved vile disgusting repulsive offensive hateful loathsome detestable abominable execrable odious horrible terrible dreadful fearful fright ful scary alarming shocking startling surprising amazing astonishing astounding bewildering confounding perplexing puzzling baffling mystifying enigmatic cryptic obscure ambiguous equivocal vague indefinite uncertain doubtful questionable problematic difficult hard tough challenging demanding strenuous arduous laborious tedious monotonous boring dull dreary gloomy dismal depressing sad sorrowful mournful melancholy doleful lugubrious funereal sepulchral deathly deadly fatal lethal mortal terminal final ultimate conclusive 